Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:10.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.82,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,To Help Somebody Someday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.78,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,We can't handle something that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.38,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, we have to \Nget the kids out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.48,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, take turns riding out of here on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.10,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.54,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:38.38,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take at least ten or twenty \Nminutes to get them all out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.80,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hold this thing back until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get near them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:52.40,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Die... All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.53,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,B-Baro? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.41,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.51,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:25.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taken responsibility \Nfor any of this yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you die until you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Also, what's your problem? \NYou're trying to kill your own brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my sword's working, \Nso I'm just gonna quickly take care of—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:47.17,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Now your anti-magic won't be \Nable to defeat him so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:51.46,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,The dark magic item I just injected \Nhim with eats the subject's life force
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.38,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,and produces an explosion of magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.78,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.94,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.74,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you got in the way again! \NQuit butting in, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.87,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in an old \Nlady whose magic's all dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.08,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got a mouth \Non you, whippersnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:36.03,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that as you get older, the magic \Nyou can generate internally weakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.53,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But the power to work with \Nthe mana that dwells
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.71,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,in nature can be increased at any age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:47.72,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I have years of experience and technique. \NI won't lose to a youngster like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.10,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate us old hags!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.97,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're an annoying \Nold lady, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.65,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you kick the bucket today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.15,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.27,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That being said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.89,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight well while protecting \Nthe kids as they escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.16,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. This is only going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.91,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Curse that Gauche! How could \Nhe run off like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.68,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.90,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm taking you back into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.03,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.79,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not only does my magic \Nnot work on that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:28.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but an insanely powerful \Nmagical monster appeared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in danger if I fight that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.36,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to the others, \Nas long as you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:39.73,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Who cares about anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:47.53,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The House of Adlai is a distinguished \Nnoble family that anyone would envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:51.45,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Little Gauche looks as \Ndignified as his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.02,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,And little Marie is as \Nbeautiful as her mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:02.23,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, about you helping me with my business...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.55,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mother and Father are dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:12.91,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They were attacked by some \Nrobbers after leaving my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.56,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's written in their will that they left
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.62,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,their fortune and everything \Nthey owned to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.19,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Every last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.02,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.40,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you guys—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.57,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.21,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:31.37,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What an impudent brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.08,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.89,flashback,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Bubby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.92,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.71,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Marie, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.88,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So as I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.88,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:57.00,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie is everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.48,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.05,flashback,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.44,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Marie is smiling,\NI don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.77,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all the cash you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:09.53,flashback,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:13.65,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And? Nobles should help out the needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.70,flashbackitalics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Only Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.74,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.77,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be paying for all of your crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.92,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You think I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.64,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:40.73,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.56,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care about other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.75,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.57,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I hate having a big brother who's so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.39,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:02.06,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that a lot of people \Ndid some awful things to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.83,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But Sister and the kids at \Nthe church are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:11.34,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I wasn't lonely when you \Nweren't with me was because of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.70,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you became a Magic Knight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.50,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's lives are connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.98,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,We're who we are because they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.53,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:32.07,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's your job as a \NMagic Knight to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:36.08,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really proud that you're a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:39.08,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please just be the cool \Nbig brother I'm proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.87,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.71,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.67,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.47,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Sister and Asta saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.88,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,That's so like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, that robe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:04.35,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Asta lent it to me so I wouldn't feel lonely \Nwhile he went to go save everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.65,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,He said it had the courage \Nof a Magic Knight in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:13.04,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I'll wait here with Marco.\NPlease go save everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:16.20,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Marie! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better mean that,\Nyou stupid little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.12,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay if anything happens to Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.53,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.21,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:26.97,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:27.97,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:29.92,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.37,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.34,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.90,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get away with Sister's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:39.09,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Asta protected us, but that \Nmonster's really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:42.97,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay! My brother's \Ngoing to fight with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:46.44,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's a Magic Knight \Njust like Asta, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.62,main,Kid 1,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.54,main,Kid 2,0000,0000,0000,,So he must be really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.65,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.66,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, make sure you stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.70,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:03.73,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.73,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.54,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta this, Asta that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.17,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about that shrimp, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:14.34,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The captain and the other squad \Nmembers wouldn't shut up about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.92,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but he immediately got caught by that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:21.73,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I'm sure he and that \Nold hag gave up and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:27.60,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it,\Npeople only care about themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:46.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet... I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.44,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.96,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop protecting them \Nand let me catch you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:58.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop protecting them? I'm a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:00.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance! Even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.85,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Is he... actually that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:15.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop protecting them? I'm a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance! Even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:24.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not going to die until \NI become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.44,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! On your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:31.49,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You yelled something stupid \Nlike "I'm not going to die,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.37,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,and then you actually almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:37.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche! Why'd you run off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.65,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:45.18,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't run. I only helped Marie escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.31,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,He finally came back, that fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.64,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.23,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.65,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You joining in isn't going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I'm going to fight... \Nfor the sake of Marie's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.05,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And so she'll say I'm cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.34,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Real Double!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Double Refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:29.77,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This monster... Magic keeps bubbling up \Nfrom it, and it regenerates immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.95,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.19,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My magic isn't even touching that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.69,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been this incompatible \Nwith an opponent since the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.00,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Should I use my trump card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:48.13,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No... No matter how strong my \Nmirror magic becomes, it won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.93,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,How lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:12.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you came to help! What are\Nyou doing charging in all by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:18.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I protect you! You protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be able to fight forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,An epic strategy, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.95,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of half-baked strategy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.57,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This guy really is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:37.38,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, {\i0}he{\i1} was \Npretty half-baked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:44.09,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to keep going? \NYou're not gonna be able to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.69,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.89,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:55.67,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she's that important, \Njoin my squad and support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.43,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.18,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an escaped convict!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.35,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:09.17,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And? I don't trust others, \Nand I only think about my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.69,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:16.29,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just protect what you want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.62,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that'll help somebody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:25.42,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, did you know this \Nwould happen someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, how many kids are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.76,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.53,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.49,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie will be sad if you all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.07,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Did Gauche just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you acting all tough for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're teammates! What else would we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid little brat! You need to \Nlearn how to talk to your seniors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.02,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And something's shining over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:06.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man! Even that didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.88,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what was that? A flying \Nanti-magic slash attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.69,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do it? How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.52,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to defeat that monster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:50.76,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,is to hit it with so many attacks at once\Nthat it doesn't have time to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.53,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The most effective strike was \Nthe slash Asta just hit it with,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.72,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but he can't launch enough of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.46,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if I used\Nmy magic on someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:06.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because Gauche had always preferred \Nto act alone and didn't trust others,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.24,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he'd never thought of using his \Nmagic to support someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:17.24,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But due to his past failures and his \Nreluctant acknowledgment of Asta,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he was able to create a spell that was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,fundamentally similar, \Nyet completely different,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.04,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and engraved a new page in his grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:30.50,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't be able to activate this \Nspell with the magic I have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.09,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me a little time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:36.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.91,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn how to treat old hags.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:44.77,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only last a minute, so make it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:52.00,main,sally,0000,0000,0000,,Leftover magic like that \Nisn't going to work at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.45,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Asta! Do that thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me! \NIf I could, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.51,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw. How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:12.42,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice. I've been hiding \Nthis, but I'll have to use it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:23.02,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the magic accumulated in \Nthe mirror magic item in my left eye
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,to activate the new spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.10,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.22,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:34.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:04.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.36,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.05,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:27.37,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that he had all \Nof his life force sucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.71,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Baro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:40.15,flashback,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.49,flashback,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep crying, Neige?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.47,flashback,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.97,flashback,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Baro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:58.26,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Baro, I won't forgive her for \Nturning you into this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:01.45,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,But the one I can't forgive most of all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:05.62,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,is myself for leaving everything to \Nhim and just doing what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:12.61,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said, I haven't taken \Nresponsibility for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:17.26,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to pay for both of our crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And when you're done \Nwith that, let's be buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can use really cool magic, \Nso you'd be really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.93,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Thank—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:48.58,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What is this immense magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.79,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt something this huge—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.04,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't... see a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:58.82,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:03.34,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,A new enemy? Are they attacking \Neverything in sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.22,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.61,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.99,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.99,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They got what they deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that appeared \Nat the enemy's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.43,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.25,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the Eye \Nof the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.25,sign_29665_280_Leader_of_the_Ey,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun\N{\fs30}Licht
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.25,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.46,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:47.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A four-leaf clover grimoire... \NJust like Yuno's?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:27.36,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:26.81,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.82,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Marie's in Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.49,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's in Danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.79,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,All right, one, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:36.42,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie! Are you an angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything when Marie's around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:43.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But there are times where I must steel \Nmy heart and decline Marie's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:44.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,For example!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:49.27,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, go back and save \NAsta and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:52.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! Going back would put you in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:57.05,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! I want to eat some \Nhot, extra-cheesy doria!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:01.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! Eating that would put \Nyour tongue in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:01.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You'll burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:06.09,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, doesn't lying \Nout in the sun feel nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:09.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No! If you're in the sun too long, \Nyour skin will be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:13.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,UV rays are a fearsome enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:16.24,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, show me a really cool spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:18.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No... Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:25.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:28.13,main,Maries,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No... Now I'm... in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:38.07,main,Maries,0000,0000,0000,,Brother? Brother? Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:42.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy who was at the \NEye of the Midnight Sun hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:45.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who attacked the Clover \NKingdom and did that to Captain Fuegoleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:47.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:51.51,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 34: \N"Light Magic vs. Dark Magic."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:54.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 34\N\N{\fs18} Light Magic VS Dark Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:53.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
